Changes in Preview-2 (2012-08-31)

- New widgets: Image, Navbar, Text, Div, Custom Header
- Support for many new properties on widgets, covering most of the documented
	jQuery Mobile features
- Support for themes from jQuery Mobile Themeroller
- Many text properties editable in-place with double-click
- Added thumbnails to projects in the project view
- Drastic improvements to drag and drop insertion/sorting, decreased flicker
- Upgraded to jQuery Mobile 1.1.0
- New plugin architecture for views derived from a common base view
- Many bug fixes and minor features
- Dropped support for web-ui-fw widgets

Changes in Preview-1 (2012-04-16)

- Initial public release
